Help.#cdata:
[Syntax: FORMAT=format] 
    
Associates a format with variables in variable-list.

[Syntax: INFORMAT=informat] 
    
Associates an informat with variables in variable-list.

[Syntax: LABEL='label'] 
    
Associates a label with variables in variable-list.

[Syntax: LENGTH=<$>length] 
    
Specifies the length of variables in variable-list.

ToolTips.@ToolTip1: Specifies that character variables can be transcoded.
ToolTips.@ToolTip2: Specifies that character variables are not transcoded.

Help.#cdata: Specifies whether character variables can be transcoded.
